imdb.plot outline: Some ancient candidates of TV Reality Show go to another country to live together in a villa (this season, they go to Miami). Their goal is to break into their professional projects. They also will have challenges to raise money for charities. Normally, in the previous seasons, new candidates arrive throughout the adventure, but this season, these candidates will live together in Las Vegas but only those who are the most successful in their professional projects will go to Miami. Those who are not successful will have to leave the adventure.
